quran[135]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,Taa Haa
  20,2,Men Telliniraali Alqur'aanaare nden e maaЙ—a fii yo a tampu
  20,3,"Si wonaa waaju wonannde on huloowo [Alla]"
  20,4,Ko Jippinaande immorde e On TaguЙ—o leydi ndin e kammuuli toowuЙ—i Й—in
  20,5,Hinnorante On O fotii ka dow Arsi kin. @Corrected
  20,6,No woodani Mo ko woni kon e kammuuli Й—in e ko woni kon e leydi nden e ko wini kon hakkunde majji kannji Й—iЙ—i e ko woni kon ka ley leydi
  20,7,"Si a fenГұinii konngol ngol, pellet, Kanko hiMo Anndi gunndoo on e ko o suuЙ—i"
  20,8,"Alla reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko, no woodani Mo InЙ—e MoЖҙЖҙe Й—en"
  20,9,taw si arii e maaЙ—a Yewtere fii Muusaa
  20,10,"Tuma nde o yi'unoo yiite, o wi'ani Й“eynguure makko nden: \"Г‘iiЙ“ee, min dey mi haynike jaynge bela-jo'o mi addanay on immorde e magge docotal maaЙ—um mi tawa ka [moggo] yiite tinndinoowo"
  20,11,"Tuma nde o arunoo e magge o noddaa; \"ko an yo Muusaa"
  20,12,"[Alla Daalano mo] Min dey ko Min Woni Joomi maaЙ—a solu paЙ—e maa Й—en; pellet an, hiЙ—a ka aynde(caatngol) Tuwaa LaЙ“Й“inaande(seninangol)"
  20,13,Min Mi SuЙ“ike ma Jento ko wonaa Wahyineede kon
  20,14,"Pellet, ko Min Woni Alla reweteeЙ—o alaa si wonaa Min Rewam; ГұiiЙ“ir e Julde nden fii Annditugol lam"
  20,15,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aroowal MiЙ—o Й—eЙ“a suuЙ—ude ngal fii yoЙ“e kala wonkii ko ki huuwi kon"
  20,16,Wata faddo ma e gaayi maggal on mo gom- Й—inaa ngal o jokki mbeleeЙ—e makko o halkii
  20,17,Ko honЙ—um woni ka Гұaamo maaЙ—a an Muusaa
  20,18,"O maaki: \"Ndun ko tuggordu am miЙ—o tuggoo ndu miЙ—o liwtirana ndu dammi am Й—in, miЙ—o mari kadi haajuuji goo e mayru"
  20,19,"O Daali: \"LiЙ“u ndu, an Muusaa"
  20,20,"O liЙ“i ndu, tawi kayru ko ndu mboddi wonundi yahude"
  20,21,"O Daali: \"Nanngu ndu wata a hulu Men artiray ndu e mbaadi mayru araniri ndin"
  20,22,Ukku junngo maaЙ—a ngon ka nder jiiba maa; ngo yaltay ko ngo raneewo ko aldaa e bone Й—um ko Aaya goo
  20,23,Fii yo Men hollle immorde e Aayeeje Amen MawЙ—e Й—en
  20,24,"Yahu ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o bewi"
  20,25,"O maaki: \"Jooma YanГұanam Й“ernde am nden"
  20,26,Newinanaa lam fiyaake am on
  20,27,Firtaa finnde nden ka Й—enngal am
  20,28,Fii yo Й“e faamu konngol am ngol
  20,29,WaЙ—anaa lam ballo jeyaaЙ—o ka Й“eynguure am
  20,30,"[Hara ko] Haaruuna musiЙ—Й—o am on"
  20,31,Semmbinir mo darnde am
  20,32,Tawnaa mo e nder fiyaake am on
  20,33,Fii yo men Senine ko Й—uuЙ—i
  20,34,Men jaЕӢtoMaa ko Й—uuЙ—i
  20,35,"Pellet, An A Wonii HumpitiiЙ—o Men"
  20,36,"O Daali: \"GomЙ—ii a okkaama toraare maaЙ—a nden an Muusaa"
  20,37,GomЙ—ii Men Neeminiino ma e laawol goo
  20,38,Tuma nde Men Wahayinnoo faade e yumma maa ko Wahayinaa kon
  20,39,"[Men Daali] Bugo mo ka nder hontoore bugoЙ—aa nden kadi ka nder diidere, yo diidere nden kadi bugoyo mo ka fonngo; Жҙetta mo gaГұo Am e gaГұo makko, Mi werlii e maaЙ—a Giggol immorde ka Am e fii yo a ne'e e dow ndenka Am"
  20,40,"Tuma nde banndiraawo maaЙ—a on yahaynoo; o wi'a: \"Enee, yo mi tinndin on e on mo no ne'a mo?\" Men artirmaa ka yumma maaЙ—a fii yo gite makko Й—en Й“uuЙ“u hara o sunaaki. WaruЙ—aa wonkii Men danndumaa immorde e saЙ—teende nden, Men jarribimaa jarrabuyeeje ГұiiЙ“uЙ—aa duuЙ“i ka yimЙ“e Madyana refti aruЙ—aa ka fodoore ko an yo Muusaa"
  20,41,Mi SuЙ“imaa fii hoore-Am
  20,42,Yahu an e musiЙ—Й—o maa on wonndude e Aayeeje Am Й—en wata on derfu e jaЕӢtagol Lam
  20,43,"Yahee ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o bewi"
  20,44,Wi'anee mo konngol newiingol bela-jo'o kanko o waajitoto maaЙ—um o hula
  20,45,"ЖҒe maaki: \"Joomi amen, menen dey meЙ—en huli nde murtata e hoore amen maa nde o bewata"
  20,46,"O Daali: \"Wata on hulu, pellet, Min MiЙ—o wonndi e mooЙ—on MiЙ—o Nana MiЙ—o Yi'a"
  20,47,"Aree ka makko, wi'on: \"Menen ko Men NulaaЙ“e Joomi maaЙ—a, accitu wonndude e amen Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en wata a leptu Й“e, gomЙ—ii men addanii ma Aaya immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a, kisiyee on wonii e on jokkuЙ—o Peewal ngal"
  20,48,"GomЙ—ii Wahayinaama e amen; wonndema, Lepte Й—en no fawii ka fennuЙ—o Й—uuri"
  20,49,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Ko an yo Muusaa, ko hommbo woni Joomi mooЙ—on"
  20,50,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Joomi amen, ko On OkkuЙ—o kala huunde tagu mayre ngun refti O Fewni"
  20,51,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Ko honno gire arane Й—en fewndori"
  20,52,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ganndal Й—um no ka Joomi am e nder Deftere, Joomi am majjataa O yejjitataa"
  20,53,"On waЙ—anЙ—o on leydi ndin weЖҙЖҙitaandi, o naadani on e nder mayri laawi, O jippini immorde e kammu ngun ndiyam Men yaltiniri Й—am nooneeji immorde e puЙ—i sertuЙ—i"
  20,54,"Г‘aamee aynon neemoraaЙ—i mo'on Й—im. Pellet, no e nder Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo] Aayeeje fii joomiraa- Й“e hakkillaaji Й—in"
  20,55,"Ko immorde e mayri Men Tagi on, ko e nder mayri Men Ruttata on, ko immorde e mayri kadi Men Yaltinoyta on laawol goo"
  20,56,"GomЙ—ii Men hollii mo Aayeeje Amen Й—en kala majje, o fenni o salii"
  20,57,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: \"Enee, a aru ka amen fii yo a yaltinir men ka leydi amen mbilaaku maaЙ—a ngun an Muusaa"
  20,58,"Maa men addane mbilewu yeru maggu, waЙ—u fodoore hakkunde amen e maaЙ—a hara men lunndataako nde wanaa an kadi [lunndotoo nde] e nokkuure fotondirnde"
  20,59,"[Muusaa] maaki: fodoore mooЙ—on nden ko Гұalnde saЙ—Й—ugol ngol, yo yimЙ“e Й“en mooЙ“indire ka walluhaa(fenynyaange)"
  20,60,Fir'awna hucciti o mooЙ“i pewje makko Й—en refti o ari
  20,61,"Muusaa maakani Й“e: \"On boniraama, wata on fefendo fenaande fawon e Alla sakko O mehira on Lepte, gomЙ—ii sooyii on fefindiiЙ—o"
  20,62,"ЖҒe pooЙ—ondiri fiyaake maЙ“Й“e on hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Й“e suuЙ—i cowndi Й—in"
  20,63,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Pellet Й“ee Й—iЙ—o ko mbileeЙ“e hiЙ“e faalaa yaltinirnde on ka leydi mon e mbilaaku maЙ“Й“e ngun Й“e itta laawol mon yeruyankeewol ngol"
  20,64,"MooЙ“itee pewje mo'on Й—en refti aron ko on lappol, gomЙ—ii malaama hannde on fooluЙ—o"
  20,65,"Muusaa maaki: \"Ko si tawii ko onon bugotoo maaЙ—un si ko menen wonata adotooЙ“e bugaade"
  20,66,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ko woni, bugee(mbedde), tawi Й“okkoy maЙ“Й“e koy e cawoy maЙ“Й“e koy no wa'itana mo sabu mbilewu maЙ“Й“e ngun woni ko e yahude"
  20,67,Muusaa so'i kulol ka wonkii makko
  20,68,"Men Daali: 'Wata a hulu, pellet ko an woni fooloowo on"
  20,69,"Bugo ko woni kon ka Гұaamo maaЙ—a Й—um moЙ—ay ko Й“e moЖҙЖҙini kon, pellet, ko Й“e moЖҙЖҙini kon ko pewje mbile bileejo on maletaake nukkuwoo ka o ardi"
  20,70,"MbileeЙ“e Й“en werlaa ko Й“e sujjuЙ“e, Й“e wi'i: \"Men gomЙ—inii Joomi Haaruuna e Muusaa"
  20,71,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: Eyoo, on gomЙ—inii mo ko adii mi duЕӢanaade(sakkitaade) on? Pelet, ko kanko woni mawЙ—o mo'on on anndinЙ—o on mbilaaku ngun, mi woondii, maa mi taЖҙa juuЙ—e mon Й—en e koyЙ—e mon Й—en taЖҙa luutindira, maa mi feta on e julle tama aray anndon ko hommbo e amen Й“uri lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e e heddotooЙ—e"
  20,72,"[MbileeЙ“e Й“en] wi'i: \"Men Й“urnataa ma e dow koo ko ari e amen immorde e Й“annganguyeeji, e On TaguЙ—o men, [an Fir'awna] Гұaawu ko Гұaawataa kon, pellet, ko Гұaawataa ko ka ngurndan aduna Й—oo"
  20,73,"Menen dey, men gomЙ—inii Joomi amen fii yo o yawtan men goopi amen e kon ko dooluЙ—aa men e mu'un immorde e mbilewu ngun, ko Alla woni MoЖҙЖҙo HeddotooЙ—o. @Corrected"
  20,74,"Pellet on mo ari ka Joomi mu'un hara ko o bonЙ—o; haray pellet, no woodani mo Jahannama o maayataa e nder magge o wuurataa kadi"
  20,75,"mo ari ka Makko ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o hara gomЙ—ii o golliino moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, haray Й“en Й—on no woodani Й“e Darjaaji ToowuЙ—i Й—in"
  20,76,"Aljannaaji Г‘iiЙ“al no doga e ley majji canЙ—i Й—in, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder ton, ko Й—um woni njoЙ“di on laЙ“Й“iniiЙ—o. @Corrected"
  20,77,"GomЙ—ii Men wahaynii faade e Muusaa roЖҙidu e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en waЙ—an Й“e laawol yooru ngol ka maayo joorngol wata a hulu hewtiteede wata a hulu [yoolagol]"
  20,78,"Fir'awna jokkitiri Й“e koneeli makko Й—in, suumi Й“e ka maayo ko suumi Й“e kon"
  20,79,"Fir'awnan majjini yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o fewnaali [Й“e]"
  20,80,"Ko onon yo Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila gomЙ—ii Men danndiino on e gaГұo mon on, Men fodi on kadi ka banЕӢe Гұaamo [fello] Tuuri ngon, Men jippini e mooЙ—on Manna= Й—acce njumri e doobe"
  20,81,"Г‘aamee immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i ko Men arsiki on kon, wota on bewu e nder mu'un sakko Tikkere Am nden jippo e mo'on, on mo Tikkere Am jippii e mu'un gomЙ—ii haray o halkike"
  20,82,"Pellet, Min ko Mi heewuЙ—o Yawtanngol wonannde on tuubuЙ—o o gomЙ—ini o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi refti o feewi"
  20,83,Ko honЙ—un heГұinmaa gaayi yimЙ“e maa Й“en an Muusaa
  20,84,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"ЖҒeeЙ—oo, hiЙ“e iwtiri Й“aawo am, mi heГұike ka MaaЙ—a Joomi fii yo A welto"
  20,85,"[Alla] Daali: \"Pellet, Mennen gomЙ—ii Men jarribike=finninii yimЙ“e maaЙ—a Й“en Й“aawo maaЙ—a, Saamiriiyu majjinii Й“e"
  20,86,"Muusaa ruttii ka yimЙ“e makko Й“en ko o tikkuЙ—o suniiЙ—o; o maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, enee, Joomi mo'on Fodaali on Fodoore MoЖҙЖҙere, kaa ko aadi ndin juutani on? Kaa on faandi nde jippotoo e mo'on Tikkere immorde ka Joomi mooЙ—on si lunndi Й—on fodoore am nden"
  20,87,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men lunndaaki fodoore maaЙ—a nden e sago amen, kono menen men ronndinaama teddeendi e cuЙ—aaje yimЙ“e Й“en men werlii Й—e, ko nii Saamiriiyu kadi welirii"
  20,88,"O yaltinani Й“e Й“anndu ngaari marn hito= huunaango, Й“e wi'i: \"Ko ko'ol woni reweteeЙ—o mon e reweteeЙ—o Muusaa on, o yejjitu [mo Й—oo]"
  20,89,"Enee, Й“ee yi'aali wonndema ruttataako e maЙ“Й“e konngol, ndi maranaa Й“e kadi lorra wonaa fii non [pooЙ—ugol] nafa"
  20,90,"GomЙ—ii Haaruuna maakaniino Й“e ko adii: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, pellet, on jarribora kol, pellet, Joomi mooЙ—on ko Hinnorante On jokkee lam Й—oftoЙ—on yamiroore am nden"
  20,91,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men seerataa ko men ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e e [dewal] makkol haa Muusaa ruttoo e amen"
  20,92,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko an yo Haaruuna, nde yi'unoЙ—aa Й“e majjii ko haЙ—umaa"
  20,93,nde jokkitataa mi? Kaa a yeddii yamaruyee am on
  20,94,"[Haaruuna] maaki: \"Ko an yo neene-gooto am, wata a nanngu waare am nden wanaa hoore am nden kadi, min dey, mi hulu wata a wi'u: Mi senndii hakkunde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, mi heЙ—aaki konngol maaЙ—a ngol"
  20,95,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko honЙ—um woni fiyaake maaЙ—a on an Saamiriiyu"
  20,96,"[Saamiriiyu] wi'i: \"Mi yi'ii ko Й“e yi'aali Й—um, mi nokki nokkannde e batte nulaaЙ—o on [Jibriila] mi werlii Й—um ko nii cuЙ—irani lam wonkii am"
  20,97,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Yahu, pellet, no woodanmaa ka ngurndam nde wowlataa wanaa meemondiral, pellet, no woodanmaa kadi Fodoore a lunndataako nde, ndaarii faade e rewteeЙ—o maa, on mo ГұalluЙ—aa ufinaade e hoore mun, mi woondii mi sunnay mo refti mi jaroo mo ka maayo e jaragol"
  20,98,"Pellet, ReweteeЙ—o mon On ko Alla, On Mo ReweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko, Ganndal Makko Yaajanii kala huunde"
  20,99,"Ko wano nii Men filloranay maa immorde e kumpital ko feЖҙЖҙunoo kon, gomЙ—ii Men addanii ma immorde ka Amen jaЕӢta"
  20,100,"Mo Й—uurike e mayre pellet, o ronndoto Г‘alnde Darngal teddeele [bakkaatu]"
  20,101,"Ko o luttinteeЙ—o e nder majje, bonanii Й“e donngal Г‘alnde Darngal"
  20,102,"Г‘alnde wuttoytee ka alaadu Men mooЙ“a bonЙ“e Й“en nden Г‘alnde ko mbuliiЙ“e [gite]"
  20,103,"HiЙ“e sowndondira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e [Й“e wi'a] on ГұiiЙ“aali si wanaa [balЙ—e] sappo"
  20,104,"Ko Menen woni AnnduЙ“e ko Й“e wowlata kon, tuma nde koohooЙ“e maЙ“Й“e e laawol wi'ata: \"On ГұiiЙ“aali si wanaa Гұallal"
  20,105,"HiЙ“e lanndaade ma fii pelle Й—en, maaku: \"Joomi am jaroto Й—e e jaragol"
  20,106,"O acca [leydi] ndin ko ndi boowal Й“owrungal"
  20,107,A yi'ataa e mayri ooГұannde wanaa tintiire
  20,108,"Ko nden Г‘alnde Й“e jokkata noddoowo on ko aldaa e selugol mo,, hitooji Й—in yankinanoo Hinnorante On hara a nanataa si wanaa nyuumbaango"
  20,109,"Nden Г‘alnde tefoore nden nafataa, si wanaa on mo Hinnorante On sakkiti Й—um O weltori konngol makko"
  20,110,Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso maЙ“Й“e e hedde Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e Й“e huЙ“indortaa Й—um ganndal
  20,111,"Geece Й—en yankinanii WuuruЙ—o DartiiЙ—o On, gomЙ—ii sooyii on ronndiiЙ—o tooГұe"
  20,112,On mo golli immorde e moЖҙЖҙi Й—in hara ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o haray o hulaa tooГұe wanaa uytaneede kadi
  20,113,Ko nii Men Telliniri nde Alqur'aanaare Aarabuure Men fensiti kadi e nder mayre immorde e kammbaaji Й—in bela-jo'o kamЙ“e Й“e hulay maa nde fuЙ—Й—anoo Й“e waaju
  20,114,"Alla LamЙ—o GoonguЙ—o On Toowii, wata a heГұor Alqur'aanaare nden ko adii nde timmintee e maaЙ—a wahayu mayre, maaku: \"Joomi Й“eydanam Ganndal"
  20,115,GomЙ—ii Men ahodiino e Aadama ko adii o yejjiti Men heЙ“anaali mo pellital
  20,116,"Tuma Nde Men Daalannoo malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en sujjanee Aadama, Й“e sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o salii"
  20,117,"Men Daali: \"Ko an yo Aadama, pellet, ooЙ—oo ko o gaГұo maa an e sonnaajo maa on, wata o yaltin on dey ka Aljanna sakko tampaa"
  20,118,"Pellet, no woodanmaa nde a weeletaake nder ton a holataa kadi"
  20,119,"Pellet, an a Й—omЙ—etaake nde ton e nguletaake kadi"
  20,120,"Seytaane sonwonsini faade e makko; o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Aadama,hara yo mi tinndine e leggal luttineede ngal e laamu ngu follotaako ngun"
  20,121,"ЖҒe Гұaami e maggal, feeГұani Й“e mettefooji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e naati e suddirgol e dow maЙ“Й“e immorde e kaaki Aljanna on, Aadama yeddi Joomi makko o majji"
  20,122,"Refti Joomi makko SuЙ“ii mo, O Tuubini mo O Fewni [mo]"
  20,123,"O Daali: \"Jippee ton, on fow mo'on, yoga e mo'on ko ayЙ“e yoga. Si tawii tun aroyii e mo'on immorde e Am Fewnoowo kala jokkuЙ—o Peewal Am ngal haray o majjataa o malkisataake kadi"
  20,124,"Kala Й—urniiЙ—o gaayi jaЕӢtagol lam, haray pellet, no woodani mo ngurndam Й“illuЙ—am Men mooЙ“oya mo Г‘alnde Darngal ko o bunЙ—o"
  20,125,"O wi'a: \"Joomi, ko fii honЙ—um mooЙ“anЙ—aa lam ko mi bunЙ—o, gomЙ—ii mi laatinoke yi'oowo"
  20,126,"O Daala: \"Ko wano nii arunoo e maaЙ—a Aayeeje Amen Й—en yejjituЙ—aa Й—e, ko wano nii kadi hannde yejjitirteЙ—aa"
  20,127,"Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“irta on fantinЙ—o hara o gomЙ—inaa Aayeeje Joomi makko Й—en, pellet, ko Lepte Laakara Й—en Й“uri saЙ—tude ko Й—en kadi heddotoo"
  20,128,"Kaa hara Й“annganaali Й“e no foti hewde ko Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e immorde e gire? HiЙ“e yaha e koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e, pellet, no e Й—um Aayeeje wonannde joomiraaЙ“e hakkillaaji Й“en"
  20,129,"Sinno wonaano Daalol aditii ngol immorde ka Joomi maaЙ—a [Lepte] Й—en laatotono duumiiЙ—e e lajal innaangal"
  20,130,"MunГұo e dow ko Й“e wowlata kon, subuhinor yettugol Joomi maaЙ—a ko adii Жҙellitagol naange ngen e ko adii mutugol magge e ka saa'iiji jemma subuhino e ka seraaji Гұallal belajo'o a weltoto"
  20,131,"Wata a yawtin dey gite maa Й—en faade kon ko Men dekmini Й—um nooneeji immorde e maЙ“Й“e, cuЙ—aari ngurndam aduna fii yo Men jarribor Й“e e Й—um, Arsike Joomi maaЙ—a on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ko on kadi heddotoo"
  20,132,"Yamir Й“eynguure maaЙ—a nden Julde nden monГұitoraa e Й—um, Men lanndaaki ma arsike ko Menen arsikaymaa. Battane [moЖҙЖҙe] Й—en kadi wonanii hulooЙ“e Alla Й“en"
  20,133,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko hanno ara e amen Aaya immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Enee, hara araali e maЙ“Й“e Й“anngal ko woni kon e Й—eri arani Й—in"
  20,134,"Sinndo Menen Men halkirno Й“e Lepte ko adii Й—um, Й“e wi'ayno: \"Joomi amen, ko hannoo Nualaa e amen NulaaЙ—o men jokka Aayeeje Maa Й—en, ko adii nde Men hoyata men hesra"
  20,135,"Maaku: \"Gooto kala [e amen] no habbitii, [onon kadi] habbitee aray anndon ko hommbo woni jom Laawol Focciingol ngol ko hommbo kadi feewi"